OL,3,CHow Avanti West Coast action during
OL,4,Cfestive period will affect passengers
OL,6,FStrike action has been announced by
OL,7,Fthe RMT union from New Year's Eve, set
OL,8,Fto cause delays and disruption for
OL,9,Fmonths into 2025.
OL,11,FAvanti West Coast services will be
OL,12,Fimpacted, with the operator announcing
OL,13,Fthis evening that the strikes will
OL,14,Ftake place after failing to agree on a
OL,15,Fdeal with the RMT.
OL,17,FAvanti has described their pay offer
OL,18,Fas very reasonable and said that they
OL,19,Fare disappointed with the train
OL,20,Fmanagers who declined their offer.
