OL,3,CHow Avanti West Coast action during
OL,4,Cfestive period will affect passengers
OL,6,FThe RMT union will strike on 31
OL,7,FDecember and 2 January. They will also
OL,8,Fbe striking every Sunday from 12
OL,9,FJanuary to 25 May 2025.
OL,11,FAvanti West Coast has said this strike
OL,12,Faction will cause significant
OL,13,Fdisruption to our customers making
OL,14,Fjourneys on the West Coast Main Line
OL,15,Fover an extended period.
