OL,3,CHow Avanti West Coast action during
OL,4,Cfestive period will affect passengers
OL,6,FA Department for Transport
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "This is incredibly
OL,8,Fdisappointing news for passengers who
OL,9,Fwould have been hoping to leave strike
OL,10,Faction in 2024, and we strongly
OL,11,Fencourage both the RMT and Avanti West
OL,12,FCoast to get back around the table and
OL,13,Fwork in good faith to resolve this as
OL,14,Fquickly as possible.
