OL,3,CHow Avanti West Coast action during
OL,4,Cfestive period will affect passengers
OL,6,F"As part of our plans to reform the
OL,7,Frailways, we're determined to move
OL,8,Ftowards a seven-day working week and
OL,9,Fend the overreliance on rest day
OL,10,Fworking, giving passengers the
OL,11,Fcertainty and reliability they
OL,12,Fdeserve."
OL,14,FThe National Union of Rail, Maritime
OL,15,Fand Transport Workers (RMT) had
OL,16,Fpreviously agreed to strike on 22,23,
OL,17,Fand 29 December, but suspended strike
OL,18,Faction after receiving a new offer
OL,19,Ffrom Avanti West Coast.
