OL,3,CHow Avanti West Coast action during
OL,4,Cfestive period will affect passengers
OL,6,FHowever, following a vote on the offer
OL,7,Fon Tuesday 17 December strikes are now
OL,8,Fset to return at the end of the month.
OL,10,FRest Day Working payments and
OL,11,Farrangements over a new technology
OL,12,Fagreement were a couple of the key
OL,13,Ffactors voted on by the RMT.
OL,15,FThe RMT has been contacted for comment.
